	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Yeah, watch for programs like ZoneAlarm that bork cookies.
<br />
<br />I've had several users report this same problem on a board I run, and was never able to reproduce the error reliably. However, completely removing the cookies used for this board then re-logging in (and choosing to remain logged in) solved the issue for them. For now anyway.
<br />
<br />Back to lurking ...

		

		</td>
